<hw>pen-friend</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person one comes to know by by
frequent friendly correspondence; a pen pal.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pen pal, pen-pal, penfriend.</syn>⟦br⟧
